---
description: Content dashboard project rules
globs: ["**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Use Next.js App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind, and shadcn/ui.
Build a dark-theme content dashboard.
Keep pages thin and extract reusable components.
Use mock data first.
Do not rewrite unrelated files.
Before coding, inspect the codebase and list files to update.